	  	  	<li>Custom cuts. Table covers are cut to finished size any shape. (see types below)</li>
	  	  	<li>Minimum order is just 5 yards.</li>
	  	  	<li>Or order by the roll. Each 54”-wide roll holds 25 yards of fabric.</li>
	  	  	<li>Finished edge sewn with 1⁄4” single turn helm</li>
	  	  </ul>
          
          <p><a href="#" class="addgray underline">Technical specs.</a></p>

        </div>

		<div class="top20">
          <a href="/styles/1"><span class="addblack"><strong>Back to ALL CLASSIC Vinyls</strong></span> <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-play"></span></a> 
        </div>        
	    <% elsif (@series.style.id == 2) %>
	  	<div>
	  	  <ul class="sideseries">
	  	  	<li>Easy care vinyls – simply wipe and go.</li>
	  	  	<li>Custom cuts. Table covers are cut to finished size any shape. (see types below)</li>
	  	  	<li>Minimum order is just 5 yards.</li>
	  	  	<li>Or order by the roll. Each 54”-wide roll holds 25 yards of fabric.</li>
	  	  	<li>Finished edge sewn with 1⁄4” single turn helm</li>
	  	  </ul>
          
          <p><a href="#" class="addgray underline">Technical specs.</a></p>

        </div>

		<div class="top20">
          <a href="/styles/2"><span class="addblack"><strong>Back to ALL PREMIUM Vinyls</strong></span> <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-play"></span></a> 
        </div>   

		<div>
          <!-- <p><a href="#">Also available for table covers. <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-play"></span></a></p> -->	
        </div> 
	    <% elsif (@series.style.id == 3) %>
	  	<div>
	  	  <p>REPEAT INFORMATION</p>
	  	    <div class="row">
			  <div class="col-sm-6">
			  	Vertical:
			  </div>
			  <div class="col-sm-6">
			    4.5"
			  </div>
			</div>
			<div class="row">
